1) This is a prime number checker application which requires a registration and login.

2) 'index.php' is the registration page. Data stores in the mysql DB installed in the instance.

3) When user clicks "Sign in here" link it directs to 'login.php', where the user need to give his registered details and hit login button.

4) 'home.php' gives the prime number application. User can enter any number and check whether a number is prime number or not.

5) Logout button is provided to the right side of the page to unset the logged in user.

6) CSS file is included for the application 'style.css'
